{"id": 1819, "genre": 1000, "title": "当代生活中，看到哪些信息后，你会在脑内自动换算一下？", "description": "或者说，你啥时候会启用你的计算能力？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 9942, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170727160736ZUzfkYsqp5a3Ht9e.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-27T17:00:12Z", "questions": [{"id": 2678, "title": "当代生活中，看到哪些信息后，你会在脑内自动换算一下？", "content": "当代生活中，看到哪些信息后，你会在脑内自动换算一下？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 225023, "content": "想吃东西的时候会自动看热量表，计算要运动多少才能消耗掉", "image": "img/option/option/20170727151459uDst7glHLr4nBEcU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225039, "content": "看到高科技产品会想“用它能省多少时间”", "image": "img/option/option/20170727154932cwlvDMjH59RSIbso.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225041, "content": "选购厨房电器的时候会默默想，做多少次可以回本", "image": "img/option/option/20170727155042qfEkyCSmTbjBQYKs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225042, "content": "看到“满199-99”类打折，会自己换算成折扣", "image": "img/option/option/20170727155147WZR13SK7rxguTqXJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225043, "content": "会仔细思考信用卡积分换里程划算还是换酒店", "image": "img/option/option/20170727155229FKOB80er9vc4qITX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225044, "content": "海淘的时候，会把价格在脑内自动加运费和税", "image": "img/option/option/201707271553544UzRcGa5kLuwJyix.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225048, "content": "旅游之前看酒店和宣传照，会自动考虑滤镜对效果的影响", "image": "img/option/option/20170727160254djoxbJS67nBF0PMC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 225050, "content": "买家具，包装上写的“方便自行组装”，我要用60-90分钟", "image": "img/option/option/20170727160639wfYr1SntL6q9ijB2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}